snippet.title: Farmers Can now Withdraw Rs 25000 Every Week, Says Shaktikanta Das

localized.description:
Farmers can now withdraw Rs 25000 every week, says Shaktikanta Das. One member of marriage families can withdraw upto 2.5 lakh rupees. There is no end to long queues at banks and ATMs. Peoples are struggling to exchange and deposit currency notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 after Modi government demonetisation decision. In Parliament winter session TMC, Congress, Left, BSP, SP and AAP are attacking Modi government over inconvenience of peoples.
